Awesome tool! I&#x27;ve always wanted to make menubar apps but never wanted to learn Xcode+ObjectiveC.<p>Related:<p>Is there no simple way to get the current temperature for location based off of GeoIP using `curl`?<p>I had to use this monstrosity to get the current temperature:<p><pre><code>    #!/bin/bash

    export PATH=&#x27;/usr/local/bin:$PATH&#x27;

    ansiweather -a off -l &#x27;San Francisco&#x27; \n      | cut -d &#x27;>&#x27; -f 2 \n      | cut -d &#x27;-&#x27; -f1 \n      | awk &#x27;{ print $1 $2 }&#x27; \n      | tr -d &#x27;C&#x27;</code></pre>
